<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-1201] Some Mahout jobs do not pass user supplied Configuration object to sub jobs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1201</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some (see patch) of our Hadoop jobs do not pass a user supplied configuration object down to sub jobs created. As a result some Hadoop related settings may not be honored.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
