                            <comment id="13645963" author="isabel" created="Tue, 30 Apr 2013 21:50:46 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Changes related to our clustering code.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13645966" author="isabel" created="Tue, 30 Apr 2013 21:51:49 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Changes related to the entropy computation stuff (make sure to apply the clustering changes first, they contain a modification to AbstractJob that is needed here as well).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13645967" author="isabel" created="Tue, 30 Apr 2013 21:52:18 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Changes related to the pfpgrowth implementation (make sure to apply the clustering changes first, they contain a modification to AbstractJob that is needed here as well).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13672240" author="gsingers" created="Sat, 1 Jun 2013 22:07:14 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;If we are marking &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1128&quot; title=&quot; MAHOUT-999 issue still actual&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MAHOUT-1128&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MAHOUT-1128&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; as dup, then we need to fix this in ClusterClassifier.readFromSeqFiles and writeToSeqFiles needs to take in a conf.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13672308" author="hudson" created="Sun, 2 Jun 2013 03:32:01 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Mahout-Quality #2027 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Mahout-Quality/2027/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Mahout-Quality/2027/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1201&quot; title=&quot;Some Mahout jobs do not pass user supplied Configuration object to sub jobs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MAHOUT-1201&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MAHOUT-1201&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Fix mahout jobs that do do not pass user supplied conf&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Some (KMeansDriver, MeanShiftCanopyDriver, FuzzyKMeansDriver, CanopyDriver,&lt;br/&gt;
ClusterClassificationDriver, PFPGrowth, DistributedConjugateGradientSolver,&lt;br/&gt;
InformationGain and InformationGainRatio) did not pass user supplied&lt;br/&gt;
configuration object to sub jobs (Revision 1488624)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;     Result = SUCCESS&lt;br/&gt;
